//sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?5,10,16 target=_blank rel=noopener>5,10,16.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?7,2,36 target=_blank rel=noopener>7,2,36.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?8,24,16 target=_blank rel=noopener>8,24,16.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,21,3 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,21,3.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,60,22 target=_blank rel=noopener>60,22.</a> <i class=sa>āśruta</i> слышимый <i class=sa>āśrutataraṃ vadati</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?2,5,11,1 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 2,5,11,1.</a>", "en_html": "— 2) to hear, perceive: <i class=sa>āśrutya vacaḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?1,19,22 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHĀG. P. 1,19,22.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?3,19,33 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,19,33.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?5,10,16 target=_blank rel=noopener>5,10,16.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?7,2,36 target=_blank rel=noopener>7,2,36.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?8,24,16 target=_blank rel=noopener>8,24,16.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,21,3 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,21,3.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,60,22 target=_blank rel=noopener>60,22.</a> <i class=sa>āśruta</i> audible <i class=sa>āśrutataraṃ vadati</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?2,5,11,1 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 2,5,11,1.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "3", "de_html": "— 3) zusagen, versprechen; mit <span class=ab>acc.</span> der Sache und <span class=ab>dat.</span> der Person<br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/1/4/40 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 1,4,40.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mugdhabodha/app1?5,15 target=_blank rel=noopener>VOP. 5,15.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanabom/app1/?2,58,27 target=_blank rel=noopener>R. ed. Bomb. 2,58,27.</a> <i class=sa>āśruta</i> zugesagt, versprochen<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/amara_dlc/app1?3,2,58 target=_blank rel=noopener>AK. 3,2,58.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/abch2/app1?1489 target=_blank rel=noopener>H. 1489.</a> <i class=sa>kuryādyathāśrutam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/yajnavalkya/app1?2,196 target=_blank rel=noopener>YĀJÑ. 2,196.</a>", "ru_html": "— 3) обещать, давать слово; с <span class=ab>acc.</span> вещи и <span class=ab>dat.</span> лица<br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/1/4/40 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 1,4,40.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mugdhabodha/app1?5,15 target=_blank rel=noopener>VOP. 5,15.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanabom/app1/?2,58,27 target=_blank rel=noopener>R. ed. Bomb. 2,58,27.</a> <i class=sa>āśruta</i> обещанный, данный в обещание<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/amara_dlc/app1?3,2,58 target=_blank rel=noopener>AK. 3,2,58.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/abch2/app1?1489 target=_blank rel=noopener>H. 1489.</a> <i class=sa>kuryādyathāśrutam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/yajnavalkya/app1?2,196 target=_blank rel=noopener>YĀJÑ. 2,196.</a>", "en_html": "— 3) to promise, assent to; with <span class=ab>acc.</span> of the thing and <span class=ab>dat.</span> of the person<br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/1/4/40 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 1,4,40.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mugdhabodha/app1?5,15 target=_blank rel=noopener>VOP. 5,15.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanabom/app1/?2,58,27 target=_blank rel=noopener>R. ed. Bomb. 2,58,27.</a> <i class=sa>āśruta</i> promised, assented to<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/amara_dlc/app1?3,2,58 target=_blank rel=noopener>AK. 3,2,58.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/abch2/app1?1489 target=_blank rel=noopener>H. 1489.</a> <i class=sa>kuryādyathāśrutam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/yajnavalkya/app1?2,196 target=_blank rel=noopener>YĀJÑ. 2,196.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "4", "de_html": "— 4) <i class=sa>āśruta = āśrāvita</i> der rituelle Zuruf<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?3,2,6 target=_blank rel=noopener>KĀTY. ŚR. 3,2,6.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?5,4,33 target=_blank rel=noopener>5,4,33.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?5,9,11 target=_blank rel=noopener>9,11.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?7,3,11,2 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 7,3,11,2.</a>", "ru_html": "— 4) <i class=sa>āśruta = āśrāvita</i> ритуальный возглас<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?3,2,6 target=_blank rel=noopener>KĀTY. ŚR. 3,2,6.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?5,4,33 target=_blank rel=noopener>5,4,33.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?5,9,11 target=_blank rel=noopener>9,11.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?7,3,11,2 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 7,3,11,2.</a>", "en_html": "— 4) <i class=sa>āśruta = āśrāvita</i> the ritual call<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?3,2,6 target=_blank rel=noopener>KĀTY. ŚR. 3,2,6.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?5,4,33 target=_blank rel=noopener>5,4,33.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?5,9,11 target=_blank rel=noopener>9,11.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?7,3,11,2 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 7,3,11,2.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "1", "de_html": "— <span class=ab>Vgl.</span> 1. <i class=sa>āśrava, āśrut, āśruti</i> . — <span class=ab>caus.</span><br> 1) verkünden, bekannt machen: <i class=sa>ā no jane śravayatam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv07.062.html#rv07.062.05 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 7,62,5.</a> <i class=sa>āśrāvayanta iva ślokamāyavaḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv01.139.html#rv01.139.03 target=_blank rel=noopener>1,139,3.</a> <i class=sa>yajñaṃ deveṣvāśrāvaya</i><br><span class=ls>ĀŚV. ŚR. 1,3,23.</span> <i class=sa>āśrāvayacca tatkarma</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mbhcalc?3.15260 target=_blank rel=noopener>MBH. 3,15260.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?5,6,17 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHĀG. P. 5,6,17.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,70,40 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,70,40</a> (<span class=ab>med.</span>). <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,73,34 target=_blank rel=noopener>73,34.</a>", "ru_html": "— <span class=ab>Vgl.</span> 1. <i class=sa>āśrava, āśrut, āśruti</i> . — <span class=ab>caus.</span><br> 1) возвещать, объявлять, делать известным: <i class=sa>ā no jane śravayatam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv07.062.html#rv07.062.05 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 7,62,5.</a> <i class=sa>āśrāvayanta iva ślokamāyavaḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv01.139.html#rv01.139.03 target=_blank rel=noopener>1,139,3.</a> <i class=sa>yajñaṃ deveṣvāśrāvaya</i><br><span class=ls>ĀŚV. ŚR. 1,3,23.</span> <i class=sa>āśrāvayacca tatkarma</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mbhcalc?3.15260 target=_blank rel=noopener>MBH. 3,15260.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?5,6,17 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHĀG. P. 5,6,17.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,70,40 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,70,40</a> (<span class=ab>med.</span>). <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,73,34 target=_blank rel=noopener>73,34.</a>", "en_html": "— <span class=ab>Vgl.</span> 1. <i class=sa>āśrava, āśrut, āśruti</i> . — <span class=ab>caus.</span><br> 1) to proclaim, make known: <i class=sa>ā no jane śravayatam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv07.062.html#rv07.062.05 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 7,62,5.</a> <i class=sa>āśrāvayanta iva ślokamāyavaḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv01.139.html#rv01.139.03 target=_blank rel=noopener>1,139,3.</a> <i class=sa>yajñaṃ deveṣvāśrāvaya</i><br><span class=ls>ĀŚV. ŚR. 1,3,23.</span> <i class=sa>āśrāvayacca tatkarma</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mbhcalc?3.15260 target=_blank rel=noopener>MBH. 3,15260.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bur/app1/?5,6,17 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHĀG. P. 5,6,17.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,70,40 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,70,40</a> (<span class=ab>med.</span>). <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,73,34 target=_blank rel=noopener>73,34.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "2", "de_html": "— 2) anreden, anrufen: <i class=sa>yo jātānyāśrāvayati ślokena</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv05.082.html#rv05.082.09 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 5,82,9.</a> <i class=sa>ā dyāṃ raveṇa pṛthivīmaśuśruvuḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.094.html#rv10.094.12 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,94,12.</a> mit <span class=ab>dopp.</span> <span class=ab>acc.</span> Jmd Etwas sagen: <i class=sa>āśrāvya rāmaṃ durvācyam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,68,29 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHĀG. P. 10,68,29.</a>", "ru_html": "— 2) обращаться к, взывать к: <i class=sa>yo jātānyāśrāvayati ślokena</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv05.082.html#rv05.082.09 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 5,82,9.</a> <i class=sa>ā dyāṃ raveṇa pṛthivīmaśuśruvuḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.094.html#rv10.094.12 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,94,12.</a> с <span class=ab>dopp.</span> <span class=ab>acc.</span> говорить кому-л. что-л.: <i class=sa>āśrāvya rāmaṃ durvācyam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,68,29 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHĀG. P. 10,68,29.</a>", "en_html": "— 2) to address, call to: <i class=sa>yo jātānyāśrāvayati ślokena</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv05.082.html#rv05.082.09 target=_blank rel=noopener>ṚV. 5,82,9.</a> <i class=sa>ā dyāṃ raveṇa pṛthivīmaśuśruvuḥ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/rvlinks/rvhymns/rv10.094.html#rv10.094.12 target=_blank rel=noopener>10,94,12.</a> with <span class=ab>dopp.</span> <span class=ab>acc.</span> to say something to someone: <i class=sa>āśrāvya rāmaṃ durvācyam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhagp_bom/app1/?10,68,29 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHĀG. P. 10,68,29.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "3", "de_html": "— 3) speciell vom rituellen Zurufen, namentlich des <i>Adhvaryu</i> an den <i>Agnīdh</i> zum Aussprechen der <i class=sa>śrauṣaṭ</i>-Formel<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/avlinks/avhymns/av09.006.html#av09.006.49 target=_blank rel=noopener>AV. 9,6,49.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/vajasasa/app1?19,24 target=_blank rel=noopener>VS. 19,24.</a> <i class=sa>ā svadhetyāśrāvayati</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyabr/app1?1,6,9,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>TBR. 1,6,9,5.</a> <i class=sa>āśrāvayetīdaṃ devāḥ śṛṇuteti</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?2,5,11,8 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 2,5,11,8.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?3,1,2,3 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,1,2,3.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,1,1 target=_blank rel=noopener>ŚAT. BR. 1,5,1,1. fgg.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,2,7 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,7.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,3,7 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,7.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?2,5,2,34 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,5,2,34.</a><br><span class=ls>ĀŚV. ŚR. 1,3,23. 4,12. 4,15,11. 9,7,9.</span> <i class=sa>omityāśrāvayati</i><br><span class=ls>CHĀND. UP. 1,1,9.</span> <i class=sa>ośrāvayetyāśrāvayanti</i><br><span class=ls>TAITT. UP. 1,1,8</span>; <span class=ab>vgl.</span><br><br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/8/2/92 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 8,2,92</a>, <i>Vārtt</i>. <i class=sa>āśrāvita</i> <span class=lex>n.</span> der rituelle Zuruf: <i class=sa>agnihotrasyāśrāvitam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyabr/app1?2,1,5,9 target=_blank rel=noopener>TBR. 2,1,5,9.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?11,4,2,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>ŚAT. BR. 11,4,2,5.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?3,3,14 target=_blank rel=noopener>KĀTY. ŚR. 3,3,14.</a>", "ru_html": "— 3) в особенности о ритуальном возгласе, в частности <i>Adhvaryu</i> к <i>Agnīdh</i> с целью произнесения формулы <i class=sa>śrauṣaṭ</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/avlinks/avhymns/av09.006.html#av09.006.49 target=_blank rel=noopener>AV. 9,6,49.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/vajasasa/app1?19,24 target=_blank rel=noopener>VS. 19,24.</a> <i class=sa>ā svadhetyāśrāvayati</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyabr/app1?1,6,9,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>TBR. 1,6,9,5.</a> <i class=sa>āśrāvayetīdaṃ devāḥ śṛṇuteti</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?2,5,11,8 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 2,5,11,8.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?3,1,2,3 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,1,2,3.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,1,1 target=_blank rel=noopener>ŚAT. BR. 1,5,1,1. fgg.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,2,7 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,7.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,3,7 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,7.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?2,5,2,34 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,5,2,34.</a><br><span class=ls>ĀŚV. ŚR. 1,3,23. 4,12. 4,15,11. 9,7,9.</span> <i class=sa>omityāśrāvayati</i><br><span class=ls>CHĀND. UP. 1,1,9.</span> <i class=sa>ośrāvayetyāśrāvayanti</i><br><span class=ls>TAITT. UP. 1,1,8</span>; <span class=ab>vgl.</span><br><br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/8/2/92 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 8,2,92</a>, <i>Vārtt</i>. <i class=sa>āśrāvita</i> <span class=lex>n.</span> ритуальный возглас: <i class=sa>agnihotrasyāśrāvitam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyabr/app1?2,1,5,9 target=_blank rel=noopener>TBR. 2,1,5,9.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?11,4,2,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>ŚAT. BR. 11,4,2,5.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?3,3,14 target=_blank rel=noopener>KĀTY. ŚR. 3,3,14.</a>", "en_html": "— 3) specifically of the ritual calling out, namely <i>Adhvaryu</i> to the <i>Agnīdh</i>, for the pronouncing of the <i class=sa>śrauṣaṭ</i> formula<br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/avlinks/avhymns/av09.006.html#av09.006.49 target=_blank rel=noopener>AV. 9,6,49.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/vajasasa/app1?19,24 target=_blank rel=noopener>VS. 19,24.</a> <i class=sa>ā svadhetyāśrāvayati</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyabr/app1?1,6,9,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>TBR. 1,6,9,5.</a> <i class=sa>āśrāvayetīdaṃ devāḥ śṛṇuteti</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?2,5,11,8 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 2,5,11,8.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?3,1,2,3 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,1,2,3.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,1,1 target=_blank rel=noopener>ŚAT. BR. 1,5,1,1. fgg.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,2,7 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,7.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?1,5,3,7 target=_blank rel=noopener>3,7.</a> <a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?2,5,2,34 target=_blank rel=noopener>2,5,2,34.</a><br><span class=ls>ĀŚV. ŚR. 1,3,23. 4,12. 4,15,11. 9,7,9.</span> <i class=sa>omityāśrāvayati</i><br><span class=ls>CHĀND. UP. 1,1,9.</span> <i class=sa>ośrāvayetyāśrāvayanti</i><br><span class=ls>TAITT. UP. 1,1,8</span>; <span class=ab>vgl.</span><br><br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/8/2/92 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 8,2,92</a>, <i>Vārtt</i>. <i class=sa>āśrāvita</i> <span class=lex>n.</span> the ritual call: <i class=sa>agnihotrasyāśrāvitam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyabr/app1?2,1,5,9 target=_blank rel=noopener>TBR. 2,1,5,9.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/shatapathabr/app1?11,4,2,5 target=_blank rel=noopener>ŚAT. BR. 11,4,2,5.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?3,3,14 target=_blank rel=noopener>KĀTY. ŚR. 3,3,14.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "4", "de_html": "— 4) herbeirufen, zu sich heranlocken: <i class=sa>parasya janam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhattikavya/app1?12,30 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHAṬṬ. 12,30.</a>", "ru_html": "— 4) призывать, подзывать к себе: <i class=sa>parasya janam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhattikavya/app1?12,30 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHAṬṬ. 12,30.</a>", "en_html": "— 4) to call hither, entice to oneself: <i class=sa>parasya janam</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/bhattikavya/app1?12,30 target=_blank rel=noopener>BHAṬṬ. 12,30.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "5", "de_html": "— 5) besprechen: <i class=sa>āśrāvita (mantra)</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?5,82,10 target=_blank rel=noopener>R. 5,82,10.</a>", "ru_html": "— 5) заклинать, нашёптывать над (кем-л.): <i class=sa>āśrāvita (mantra)</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?5,82,10 target=_blank rel=noopener>R. 5,82,10.</a>", "en_html": "— 5) to discuss, talk over: <i class=sa>āśrāvita (mantra)</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/ramayanagorr/?5,82,10 target=_blank rel=noopener>R. 5,82,10.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}, {"tag": "6", "de_html": "— <span class=ab>Vgl.</span> <i class=sa>āśrāvaṇa</i> . — <span class=ab>desid.</span> <i class=sa>āśuśrūṣati</i> (nicht <i class=sa>˚te</i>)<br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/1/3/59 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 1,3,59.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mugdhabodha/app1?23,57 target=_blank rel=noopener>VOP. 23,57.</a>", "ru_html": "— <span class=ab>Vgl.</span> <i class=sa>āśrāvaṇa</i> . — <span class=ab>desid.</span> <i class=sa>āśuśrūṣati</i> (nicht <i class=sa>˚te</i>)<br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/1/3/59 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 1,3,59.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mugdhabodha/app1?23,57 target=_blank rel=noopener>VOP. 23,57.</a>", "en_html": "— <span class=ab>Vgl.</span> <i class=sa>āśrāvaṇa</i> . — <span class=ab>desid.</span> <i class=sa>āśuśrūṣati</i> (not <i class=sa>˚te</i>)<br><a class=ls href=https://ashtadhyayi.com/sutraani/1/3/59 target=_blank rel=noopener>P. 1,3,59.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/mugdhabodha/app1?23,57 target=_blank rel=noopener>VOP. 23,57.</a>", "dcs": null, "src": "attested"}]}, {"key": "_sru~~h0_08_praty_a", "h": "pratyāśru", "iast": "pratyāśru", "senses": [{"tag": "1", "de_html": "— <i class=sa>pratyā</i>, <span class=ab>partic.</span> <i class=sa>˚śruta</i> <span class=lex>n.</span> = <i class=sa>pratyāśrāvita</i><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/taittiriyas/app1?7,3,11,2 target=_blank rel=noopener>TS. 7,3,11,2.</a><br><a class=ls href=https://sanskrit-lexicon-scans.github.io/katyasr/app1?3,2,6 target=_blank rel=noopener>KĀTY. 